<section>
  <h2>Our Story</h2>
  <p>
    In 2020, a small group of volunteers in Nairobi saw a need — children living without access to food, shelter, or education.
    We began helping just one family. Today, with your help, we've changed the lives of **over 1,000 children** in Kenya.
  </p>
  <p>
    With the donations received, we've built classrooms, provided clean water, distributed food packs, and supported mothers in setting up small businesses.
    Each shilling donated brought new hope.  
  </p>
  <p>
    One unforgettable moment: In 2022, a newborn named Amani was saved from severe malnutrition after a community alert — your support funded her nutrition, housing, and education. Today, she is a joyful, healthy 3-year-old.
  </p>

  <a href="tel:+254728275422" class="donate-button">Donate via M-Pesa: 0728275422</a>
</section>

